text.tspan: Net enrolment rates in lower secondary education, adjusted gender

An
adjusted gender parity index
of 1 indicates equal net enrollment rates in
lower secondary
school between boys and
girls. Values below 1 favor boys, and above 1 favor girls.
Data source: UNESCO Institute for Statistics (2025)
